snippet.title: Winter Survival Simulator | Devs Play
snippet.description:
Watch "Devs Play" with Mercus - Lead Programmer at DRAGO Entertainment, who will play the Winter Survival Simulator demo.

If you haven't played Winter Survival Simulator yet, check it out on Steam and add it to your wishlist.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394960/Winter_Survival_Simulator/

You can find us on: 
Discord - https://discord.gg/qQx7aKq
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/wintersurvivalsimulator
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/wintersurvivalsimulator/
